map editor, World Weaver. Utilising the latest tech advancements, this editor will intelligently build a map from your exact play-space dimensions to create a one-of-a-kind map that you and your friends can battle on.", "short_description": "Turn any playspace into the ultimate multiplayer combat arena in TritonVR 2! Using cutting-edge tech, TritonVR 2 allows you to turn any area into a battlefield, with up to 4 players simultaneously able to compete in the action."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.tetrastudios.com.au/privacypolicy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Tetra Studios", "support_website_url": "https://www.tetrastudios.com.au/contact", "website_url": "https://www.tetrastudios.com.au/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "3744040075834813"}, {"id": "644354873106712"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "6874326265990615"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1139297081234469"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "883813249964350"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1139297081234469"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1733523840, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1139297081234469"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8949119251844629", "version": "1.9.3"}, "id": "260816166552950", "